commit.message:
Reshuffle locations to better encapsulate repository structure (#988)

* introduce and reshuffle init and check location methods
* unify get_fs_abilities
* introduce setup location method for shadows
* get rid of Globals.rbdir
* move creation methods to shadow
* Remove parameters about directory structure from most repository shadow functions
* Remove parameters about directory structure from most directory shadow functions
* Move log functions to repo shadow side
* Move get_parsed_time to shadow repo
* Reshuffle imports for connections to avoid circular dependencies
* Introduce location module to avoid circular dependencies by implicit loading of package __init__
* Move regress and get_increments functions to shadow repo
* Move method setup_quoting to repo shadow
* Move _get_removal_time from remove action to repo shadow
* Replace remote_transfer through local_transfer for simpler logic
* Add setup_logging method to shadow repo and re-order with quoting
* Fix security tests for update-only
* Reshuffle again setup, replacing setup_quoting and setup_logging with setup_finish
* Move init_owners_mapping to shadow's setup
* All mapping file parameters are converted to strings from the beginning.
